setPingIntervalBlock

public void setPingIntervalBlock(int pingInterval)
(Re)setting a ping interval block. If a ping interval block is already present within the packet, it is replaced by a new one with the new ping value. If n o ping interval block is present within the packet, a new block is added.

Parameters:
pingInterval - the ping interval to set.
